-
    const data = {
        assetsVersion: 35,
        googleAnalyticsId: 'UA-xxxxxx-1',
        pageFavicon: {
            href: 'assets/images/ada-logo.png',
            type: 'image/png'
        },
        pageTitle: "ADA 2018 - Exploring customer behavior on Amazon"
    }

doctype html
html
    head
        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no')
        title= data.pageTitle
        link(rel='icon', href=data.pageFavicon.href, type=data.pageFavicon.type)

        link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Indie+Flower", rel="stylesheet")
        link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Zilla+Slab", rel="stylesheet")
        link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Sacramento", rel="stylesheet")
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='styles.css?' + data.assetsVersion)

        script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/0cebcc1cf0.js')

        script(async, src='https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=' + data.googleAnalyticsId)
        script
            | window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
            | function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
            | gtag('js', new Date());
            | gtag('config', '#{data.googleAnalyticsId}');
    body

        div#static-header.static-header-hidden
            img(src="assets/images/ada-logo.png")
            h1 ADA 2018

        div#page-content

            div#page-header.page-bloc
                h1#page-title Exploring customer behavior on Amazon
                p
                    | Started 20 years ago, Amazon completely reshaped the online market.
                    | Amazon has more than half a billion different products within very diversified categories (book, kitchen equipment, jewelry..).
                    | This growth had an impact on how people sell and buy on the platform.
                    | Because there are so many products, we might think that customer reviews have a crucial importance on the choices customer make before buying a product.
                p
                    | Because customer reviews are a form of social interaction within the online marketplace, we aim to find out in what way customer reviews are relevant, and what is their overall influence on the product success.
                    | Is a first bad review a red flag for customers?
                p
                    | In the first steps of our analysis, we explored many aspects of our data, and we thought it is a good idea to work on every category of products separately, since our analysis is mainly textual, every category has its own lexical aspects to conserve, and then compare the overall behavior.

                br

                p.links
                    a(href="https://github.com/aminetourari", target="_blank") Mohammed Amine TOURARI
                    a(href="https://benjamin-raymond.pro", target="_blank") Benjamin RAYMOND
                    a(href="https://github.com/youssefkit", target="_blank") Youssef KITANE

                p.links
                    a(href="https://github.com/epfl-ada-project-amazon/data-analysis", target="_blank")
                        | See on github
            hr.page-separator

            div#page-body

                div#page-tab-controls
                    div.tab-select
                        input.tab-select-radio(id=`cat-1`, type="radio", name="tab-select", value=0, checked="checked")
                        label(for=`cat-1`) Pets supplies
                    div.tab-select
                        input.tab-select-radio(id=`cat-2`, type="radio", name="tab-select", value=1)
                        label(for=`cat-2`) Home & kitchen
                    div.tab-select
                        input.tab-select-radio(id=`cat-3`, type="radio", name="tab-select", value=2)
                        label(for=`cat-3`) Video games

                div#page-tabs
                    div#tab-0.page-tab.tab-hidden
                        include tabs/cat1
                    div#tab-1.page-tab.tab-hidden
                        include tabs/cat2
                    div#tab-2.page-tab.tab-hidden
                        include tabs/cat3


    script(src='bundle.js?' + data.assetsVersion)
